Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 14, 2026, the following bill was signed into law;
H.B. NO. 2001, H.D. 2, S.D. 1 RELATING TO LOVE MY LIBRARY DAY.
